title: 17 Minute of Lords of the Fallen Extended Gameplay Presentation
description:
Check out an extended look at a gameplay in Lords of the Fallen. We get a look at various locations you'll be fighting through, as well as a few bosses.

Lords of the Fallen releases Friday 13th October.

A vast world awaits in all-new, dark fantasy action-RPG, Lords of the Fallen. As one of the fabled Dark Crusaders, embark on an epic quest to overthrow Adyr, the demon God. 

"Gameplay footage not final: Visuals are subject to change"
